description.text: Available for short or long term stay! This stunning 2-story, 3-bedroom luxury apartment unit in Brentwood is the epitome of refined living. The unit is fully furnished and equipped with everything you need for a comfortable and lavish stay. The spacious and stylish living room opens up to a fully equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances. The kitchen is complete with a refrigerator, oven, stovetop, dishwasher, and microwave, Nespresso coffee maker, and plenty of cabinet space for all your cooking essentials. The apartment features three bedrooms. The primary bedroom boasts a king-sized bed, a large walk-in closet, and a private balcony on the second floor. There is another bedroom on the second floor and the third bedroom is located on the first floor. The apartment also comes with a designated workspace. Other amenities include central air conditioning, in-unit laundry, and high-speed internet access. The building also offers a fitness center, conference room, rooftop terrace, and a 24-hour doorman for added convenience and security.This fully furnished luxury apartment in Brentwood is the perfect place for anyone looking for a lavish and convenient living experience. With its prime location, stylish furnishings, and modern amenities, you'll have everything you need for a comfortable and enjoyable stay. You are also within walking distance to coffee shops like Alfreds and Joe and the Juice, Whole Foods, and various restaurants.

Sleeping Arrangements - King Bed, 70.8in/180cm Amenities Building amenities unique to this one-bedroom include an on-site: - Dryer - Gym - Washing machine - Parking - Pets allowed Arrival and ongoing support The entire apartment is yours to enjoy! You'll either be personally greeted by a Blueground team member or given self check-in instructions. Throughout your stay, you'll have access to our Client Experience team through the Blueground App. You can schedule additional cleanings, submit maintenance requests, and view our neighborhood recommendations with just a few taps. We'll share all details upon confirmation of your stay. Ideally Located This furnished apartment is located in Brentwood, a small area on the Westside of Los Angeles. It is well-known for being one of the wealthiest in the county. The quiet neighborhood features tree-lined streets and impressive, upscale homes. San Vicente Boulevard is the main thoroughfare and is full of Italian eateries and cozy cafes. In addition, the Getty Center museum is also located in Brentwood and offers a world-class art collection that is ideal for culture lovers. Other things to note Building amenities may have an extra cost. This Blueground apartment has flexible lease options, allowing you to book it for one month, a year, or more. Pets are welcome, though weight limits and breed restrictions apply and may incur fees. Parking is offered based on availability and is subject to a fee. Please keep in mind that this is a walk up building. We take great pride in ensuring every photo displayed is shot in our own apartments with our actual furnishings. That said, we regularly refresh our decor and furniture arrangement, which may differ from what's pictured.

Welcome to your ideal summer retreat at 231 S. Thurston Avenue! This delightful and impeccably maintained home, located in the sought-after Westwood Hills neighborhood, offers a fantastic furnished rental opportunity. Perched high above the street, this charming residence boasts 3 bedrooms and 3.25 bathrooms, ensuring everyone has their own private oasis. Includes Wolf stove, Bosch dishwasher and Miele washer and dryer. Throughout the home, you'll be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors that exude warmth and character. Equipped with HVAC to keep you cool during the summer months. Unwind on the inviting patio, creating the perfect setting for outdoor relaxation and enjoyment. Available for summer lease June 1-September 4, 2023.

Situated in the coveted Bel Air Skycrest neighborhood, this elegantly modern yet traditional-style home was envisioned for grand-scale living and entertaining. Capturing panoramic city, canyon, and mountain views, the home seamlessly blends indoor and outdoor living, offering the ideal space to host family and friends.Arrive to the private drive, where the ivy-clad facade and lush landscaping frame the towering, arched front door. Enter into the magnificent formal living and dining room with soaring 30-foot ceilings, an entertainer's bar, regal fireplace and floor-to-ceiling arched windows and glass doors framing views of the property and mountains beyond. Off the entertaining space is the expansive gourmet chef's kitchen with spacious island, premier Viking appliances and an adjacent family room with fireplace. Glass doors connect living and entertaining spaces to the extraordinary backyard retreat, where tall palms and mature trees hold court over the swimming pool, heated spa, built-in BBQ kitchen and grass yard. Expansive terraces and a covered loggia offer ample space for lounging, dining and entertaining amidst the far-reaching views.Completing the first floor is a plush home theater with a wet bar and an office that may serve as an additional bedroom or staff quarters. Stairs ascend to the sweeping terraced hallway, which overlooks the living room below. At one end, find three bedrooms, each with ensuite baths and walk-in closets, and on the other, the stunning primary suite, boasting a wet bar with fridge, soaring ceiling, marble fireplace, soaking tub and balcony with fantastic views.Featuring a 2-car garage and plenty of additional parking, the home offers a quiet, tranquil setting in a central location close to the Westside and L.A.'s best private schools, including Curtis, Buckley, Mirman and Milken. With convenient nearby access to the 405, the home is minutes from Brentwood, Beverly Hills, Santa Monica and the Valley.

Pristine contemporary style built 2011. Luxury 3BR + 2 baths in the heart of Brentwood, walk to Ralphs, shops & restaurants. Gourmet kitchen has stainless steel appliances, quartz counter tops, elegant glass tiled backsplash & spacious pantry. Gorgeous wide hardwood floors throughout. Custom shutters in all sliding glass doors. Huge master suite has built-in walk in closet & separate linen closet. Beautifully appointed master & 2nd bath. Installed flat screen TV in the living room. Inside washer/dryer. Easy access to elevator, gym and trash chute. Best of all, no neighbor on either side of this unit-quiet and private. Rooftop sundeck is perfect for entertaining-has wet bar & outdoor furniture. A fully equipped gym is open 24 hours. Minutes to Santa Monica and Beverly Hills. .

Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac and secluded behind privacy fencing, 800 Bramble Way is a stunning Mid Century home with 3-bedrooms, 3-bathrooms and a spacious backyard with pool and spa. With skylights throughout and the entire back of the home made of glass, the spacious open floor plan is flooded with natural light. Terracotta floor tiles lead you through under high vaulted ceilings covered in wood. The sunswept kitchen offers views of the backyard, stone countertops, stainless steel appliances, a seated island, and breakfast nook. Adjacent to the kitchen is the dining room and steps leading to a sunken living room with a floor-to-ceiling fireplace. Each of the home's secondary bedrooms have skylights and one has an en suite bath. The expansive primary suite is a private retreat with access to the backyard through sliding glass doors, a built-in reading nook, abundant storage and spa-like bath with dual vanities and a jetted tub. Outside, the backyard offers a true oasis with a sparkling pool and spa surrounded by lush, mature bamboo and other foliage. Whether you're taking a dip in the pool, lounging on the stone patio or playing on the turf lawn, the backyard is the ideal space for unwinding and enjoying Southern California's year-round sunshine. The property also comes complete with a 2-car garage with a washer and dryer and ample storage space. Combining an idyllic location with timeless Mid Century characteristics, this tranquil Los Angeles home is conveniently located yet seemingly a world away.

This spacious 3-bedroom apartment located in the heart of Brentwood offers over 2, 100 square feet of living space. Situated in a small 8-unit building constructed in 2006, this unit features an elevator that takes you to a semi-private foyer. Designed as a single-level unit, allowing plenty of natural light to fill the space. With no shared walls and only two units per floor, you can enjoy a sense of privacy and tranquility. The true highlight of the apartment is the gourmet kitchen, equipped with high-end Viking Stainless Steel appliances and a breakfast area. The beautiful wide-planked hardwood floors add to the luxurious feel of the space. The carpet in the bedrooms will be replaced with wood flooring. The large living room boasts a cozy fireplace and a balcony for taking in the beautiful surroundings. The massive master suite is a true retreat, complete with a separate sitting area, balcony, three closets (including a walk-in), and a spacious master bath. Additional details such as crown molding, plantation shutters, and great storage add to the functionality and elegance of the apartment. Conveniently located within walking distance of all of your favorite shops and restaurants, this apartment is perfect for anyone seeking a luxurious and convenient lifestyle. Gated and covered, secured parking. Available immediately.

A gated drive and courtyard entry leads to this authentic Spanish masterpiece on one of the most desirable streets in Brentwood. Perfect combination of old world elegance and modern day functionality, along with total privacy. Currently tenant occupied until mid-June, and photos are from before the current tenancy. Privately situated in the exclusive Moraga Estates guard-gated community in Bel Air, this ground-up, newly built mansion is the epitome of luxury. With peaceful views of the manicured gardens, pool, and mountains, this French inspired estate was meticulously designed to satisfy Feng Shui principles and built with quality comparable to the traditional chateaus. With over 18, 000 square feet the estate boasts the finest finishes throughout sourcing antique materials from Europe; the French antique light fixtures, doors and windows, and the 18th century, wood-burning fireplaces are art pieces in themselves. Through the dramatic entry with soaring 30' ceilings and a grand staircase, the formal living room with equally high ceilings leads into the backyard with a sparkling infinity edge pool and spa, mature landscaping, and a lanai with an outdoor bar and fireplace. In a world of its own surrounded by greenery, the exquisite master suite features incredible wood detail, 18' high ceilings, dual closets, a bathroom fit for a queen, and an expansive terrace to enjoy morning coffee. Among others, amenities include a beautiful library, a massive soundproof gym/spa flex space that could be converted to a music studio, an architecturally stunning staircase that leads into the basement to enjoy the home theater and entertainment space. In addition to the detail experienced at every turn, this property includes a 3 car garage with high ceilings allowing space for a lift to house up to 6 cars, and a fully detached two bedroom guest house. This French Chateau must be seen to truly recognize the detail and beauty of this once in a lifetime estate. Also available for short term lease!

The second half of the house features 3 bedrooms of similar size with bright windows, great closets and ample space for bedroom furniture and they share a huge, newly renovated bathroom with glass shower, separate tub and double sink. The Master Bedroom is at the end of the hall with a sliding glass door leading to the patio, windows with views of the canyon, 3 closets, and a spa-like en-suite master bathroom with dual sinks, glass shower, and large window flooding it with light. Since then, invited artists have brushed the property with their artistic strokes further enhancing the creative environment. Set amongst the backdrop of the Santa Monica conservancy in Brentwood, the nearly 2-acre property is surrounded by spectacular cactus gardens, trickling fountains, meandering trails, towering palm trees and an array of wide open spaces designed to provide ultimate relaxation. The gated compound consists of a single-level 5750 Square Ft Ranch house, a 600 Sq Ft 1-bedroom guest house and a meditation studio sitting atop the property and looking down onto the billowing landscape below. The main house offers 3 bedrooms on opposing sides of the house, including a primary suite overlooking the pool & grounds, 4.5 bathrooms, a fabulous farm-style eat-in kitchen w/center island, formal dining room, living room, library, den and numerous fireplaces creating a warm ambience. High ceilings and windows surround the dwelling for views of the outdoors from every direction. Outdoor spaces include a large covered patio for lounging & dining, outdoor BBQ area and a salt-water pool with heath ceramics and a diving board. You must agree to share your space with the local wildlife, owls hooting, falcons, parakeets and humming birds carry on, while bicyclists wind their way up and down the peaceful slope of Mandeville Canyon. Great neighbors you will never see! Inquire for lease terms up to 1-year, offered furnished only. Available mid June 2023. Shown by appointment only.

Welcome to 12320 Montana Ave. This beautiful 2 Bed + 2.5 Bath is available for lease! Recently renovated, this property is located directly across the street from the Brentwood Country Club. Residence 203 is located on the 3rd floor of the building with a large kitchen that opens up into the dining area and living room. The residence is South facing, with a large balcony in the living room. Recessed lighting throughout and large windows to let in lots of natural light. Bathrooms have large showers and a soaking tub. Large walk-in closet in the master bedroom. Owner paid utilities include water and trash. This is a controlled access property with a covered parking garage and assigned parking. Stainless steel appliances, in-unit washer/dryer, central air-conditioning and heat. Schedule your tour today!

This spacious luxury penthouse unit is available with a 12-month lease terms. The IMPERIA features keyless entry and offers one bedroom and one bathroom with private single suite configuration and a luxury bathroom with tub. The open concept designer kitchen and dining area leads into the central living room with built-in glass covered credenza. An interior patio or balcony complements the floor plan allowing for serene courtyard garden views. Villa Bel Air offers residents an array of modern amenities to level-up your lifestyle including a gym with top-tier equipment, central courtyard with fireplace, and a work lounge with state-of-the-art ROOM pods for conferencing and private meetings. Unwind by the koi pond in the lushly landscaped garden, bask in the sunshine at the outdoor penthouse lounge, or hit the grill area for an al fresco culinary adventure.

Traditional Westwood Hills home was delicately renovated to balance its original 1940's architecture with today's comforts. Relish coming home to a delightful, bright, and vibrant retreat accentuated with designer finishes, stylish lighting, and wonderful indoor/outdoor flow. The home features a gas-burning fireplace in the living room, three bedrooms upstairs, one bedroom downstairs ideal for guests or office, hardwood floors throughout, central AC, formal dining room, and an exquisitely designed kitchen with a concealed Sub-Zero refrigerator, Wolf range, dishwasher, and wine fridge. Inviting backyard with multiple areas for entertaining or simply relaxing makes this the perfect setting to enjoy time with your guests. The courtyard offers a beautifully designed pergola with wall mounted heat lamps, outdoor TV area, and access to an open-air BBQ and kitchen island. To complete this splendid garden is an L-shaped built-in bench, which surrounds the fire pit to ensure the area feels clean and modern, yet welcoming. Property has beautiful curb appeal; it's situated on a quiet street in a highly desirable neighborhood with great schools and within close proximity to Brentwood and Westwood Village.

One story, this lovely family home is filled with natural light throughout, a cozy fireplace, gracious dining area, and beautiful entertainer's deck, with views of The Getty Center. Leading back into the kitchen from the secondary deck you'll will find top-of-the-line appliances. Spacious bedrooms with custom blinds for privacy. Serene neighborhood with award-winning schools, and a great location! Including upgrades fresh landscaping and new driveway. 4 parking spots available, 2 outdoor near the gate and 2 in the garage.

This three story smart home is light and bright with open floor plan, and expansive views. Close to the Getty and centrally located to 405, Santa Monica & Beverly Hills. Formal living and dining rooms, Large chefs kitchen with adjoining family room, with an elevator to all floors. Exceptional master retreat complete with sitting room and double-sided fireplace, large private veranda, his/hers bathrooms, walk-in closets. En Suite Bedrooms take in views of nature and golf course. Ideal for lounging and entertaining is an expansive theater, game& billards room. Relaxing sun-drenched backyard with an infinity-edge pool, spa, veranda and outdoor cooking area. Located in a private cul-de-sac location. description.text: Gorgeous front facing unit in one of the most recently constructed and modern buildings in prime Brentwood! This unit offers 3 bedrooms plus a den and, 3 bathrooms. Open floor plan with great natural light, Oak wood floors in the living areas and romantic fireplace. Gourmet kitchen with quartz counters, custom Oak cabinets, stainless steel appliances, Grohe fixtures, and breakfast bar open to the dining and living areas. Main suite with walk in closet and beautiful contemporary bathroom. Generous outdoor space of the living room and bedrooms. Freshly painted. Inside laundry. The community amenities include, gated parking with additional guest parking, sun drenched furnished community roof top sun deck. Prime location near shops and dining along trendy San Vicente and minutes away from Brentwood's Farmer's Market.

Open and bright rear unit of a perfectly located and just remodeled Brentwood duplex. It has a very large living room, dining area and bedrooms. Brand new Hardwood floors and Central HVAC. Outside has fenced/private rear yard. Light and bright Bedrooms, recessed LED lighting throughout and generous closet space with shelving. New dual-pane windows and plantation shutters. The eat-in kitchen was remodeled with granite countertops. The bathroom also features granite countertop and a separate tub and shower. Washer and Dryer in the Unit. 1 Car Parking located in garage and 1 Car Parking Uncovered. Washer and Dryer are located inside the unit. Very close to Brentwood Village and UCLA. Please, do not disturb the occupants.

Short term unfurnished lease. A chance to live on one of Brentwood's most coveted and premier streets. This 16, 349 sq. ft. flat lot (per public records) presents an extraordinary opportunity for short term or location filming. 3, 457 sq ft, 6 bedroom, 4 bath, 1946 Farm House. This property has a dramatic 112 ft. frontage, and the home is elegantly set back from the street. A secluded magical old-style backyard awaits you, reminiscent of a bygone era, with mature landscaping and room to run and play. The inviting pool is situated at the back of the grounds. This is truly a unique property graced with timeless charm and endless possibilities. Call listing agent for full details.

Chic and stylish duplex with a separate entrance, front and back yard. Nestled right in the perfect residential neighborhood, you'll love the incredible schools, proximity to the Brentwood Country Club and easy commute to dining, shopping, and entertainment. Bright and airy with a thoughtful flow, you'll find that every detail has been considered in this gorgeous remodel. High-end finishes, designer furniture, and top-of-the-line appliances make this beauty a true treat to call home. A newly-installed heating and air conditioning system and brand-new windows and blinds keep you comfortable year-round. Available for one year and with short-term options.

Top floor and turn key 2 bedroom, 2 bath with soaring 10 foot ceilings, lovely light and spacious room proportions. Ideal floor plan with dedicated dining, spacious living room and split bedroom layout. Beautiful hardwood floors throughout, recessed lighting, high end finishes, granite countertops, dishwasher, microwave, stainless steel appliances. This unit also features a generous private balcony, gas fireplace, and in-unit washer and dryer. The meticulously maintained unit features a fountained courtyard and two tandem dedicated parking spots. Centrally located in the heart of Brentwood near the farmers market, Brentwood golf course and track, shops, dining, grocery and easy access to transit. Owner pays for trash and maintenance. No dogs allowed. Cats upon approval with a $500 duct cleaning fee. Excellent financials and credit (760+) $25.00 application fee via personal check.

This sustainable Mandeville Canyon home is a stunning example of site-specific modernism by architect Jesse Bornstein AIA. The 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath main house, 1 bed 1 bath guest house, lap pool & spa, seamlessly connect to the lush natural surroundings. Timeless materials like hardwoods, polished concrete, and gypsum plaster blend with massive glass walls and retractable sliding doors to create a dramatic, livable space that interacts with the landscape and superb natural sunlight. The home features a gorgeous living room and dining space with 20-foot ceilings and a double-sided fireplace, a gourmet kitchen with a center island, and an outdoor dining area. The upper wing houses the primary suite with a fireplace, his/her closet, and a Zen bath behind Shoji glass panels, while the opposite wing has an open den and two spacious guest bedrooms with a full bath. Custom details include indirect recessed lighting, granite, flagstone, built-in speakers, seating, and a security system.

This stately home is located in a quaint and charming neighborhood of lower Bel Air. It exudes tons of character and is situated on serene grounds offering a peaceful oasis. Renovated and lovingly restored with many original features, this stunning traditional home features hardwood floors, large size living room with fireplace, built-in shelving, and lots of windows. Gorgeous wood-paneled den, formal dining room with wainscoting and built-in shelves. Kitchen has circular booth seating with direct access to the maids quarters. Includes a luxurious master suite with walk-in closet. Gorgeous grounds are designed for entertaining, with brick covered patio and waterfall to create a magical evening. This home is centrally located, a short drive from Westwood/UCLA, Beverly Hills, and the San Fernando Valley.

Welcome to Brentwood's most charming 3-bed and 2-bath home! This beautiful California cottage comes complete with hardwood floors and natural light throughout! Home includes a formal living room with a fireplace to cozy up to and a kitchen perfect for hosting a dinner party with friends! The garage is an additional living space as it has been converted to an extra bedroom! Home comes fully furnished and looking for a great tenant! The yard is complete with lush grass and a pool perfect for these hot summer days! Within the Kenter Canyon School boundary. Don't wait!

description.text: With a harmonious indoor/outdoor flow, this rustic modern architectural home in prime lower Bel Air is a peaceful oasis within close proximity to all things Los Angeles. This exceptional gated estate sits on half an acre of park like grounds. A private driveway will lead you to the estate, encompassing a main house with romantic casita and courtyard. One feels being far away in a camp resort, yet only 2 minutes from the freeway. The home's central location makes everything within a 10 minute drive, such as Beverly Hills, Santa Monica, and the Valley. The home is also close to private school row. Inspirational and practical, the open floor plan seamlessly connects light filled spaces for easy living. With romantic high-pitched ceilings, a fireplace, private balcony, and walk-in closet, the master suite is like no other. The highlight of the home is the backyard, which is like Disneyland for children and adults alike. Above the sparkling salt water pool and spa is an expansive grassy lawn for playing lacrosse. Amongst the mature oak trees, there are areas for relaxation and leisure, such as a treehouse, hammock area, and kids' tent area. There is also a charming outdoor dining area-the perfect place to entertain day or night, while watching children play by an adjacent sport court. Combining art, design and functionality, this masterpiece elevates daily life to a whole new level. This home offers privacy and upscale, yet comfortable and convenient living, all in one.

Available Late June. 3 month minimum, long term welcomed. Wonderfully appointed two story home in quiet upscale Brentwood neighborhood. 5 bedrooms up including large master with walk in closet and attached large office space overlooking pool/backyard and one bedroom down with private entrance. 2 car garage. Fully stocked kitchen, outdoor BBQ, 6 flat screen TV's, heated swimming pool, hot tub, basketball court, private patios, two car garage, secure gated entrance with call box, and much more. Gated driveway and gated walk in entrance. Private fenced in yard, Private enclosed backyard. Wonderful neighborhood, walk to restaurants and shops along San Vicente Blvd. (Current Furniture/furniture layout may be different from what is shown in listing pics)

BEST ADDRESS IN TOWN! Within walking distance of the Brentwood Country Mart and Brentwood Country Club, easy access to the 405, and just a few minutes' drive from Caruso's Palisades Village, this charming garden estate is guarded by old Magnolias and a 125 foot rolling front lawn. An enchanting home with a summer-vacation ambience. Chic living and dining rooms with sunny bay windows show off expansive front gardens. A stunning great room with French doors (and vintage European metal hardware) opens to a very large brick patio with a spectacular view of the lush and large back yard. The quintessential setting for hosting spontaneous gatherings or major entertainment events. Three generous en-suite bedrooms on one wing. The primary is a lovely sanctuary with fireplace; tall windows and glass doors reveal the astonishingly beautiful gardens. With a simple u-shaped floor plan, vintage hardwood floors, sun-drenched rooms surrounded by exquisite landscaping, a lap pool and hundreds of rose bushes, this is a highly desirable, unique retreat for a sophisticated renter. Located on one of the most beautiful corners in the Park, it will take your breath away.
